							</div>
													<div class="Grid Grid--with-gutter d:f@md p-b:4">
								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											And I say, &quot;Cate, what do you want to do?&quot; (Laughter)
											&quot;You&#39;re a great actor, and I like to give to my actors —
											why don&#39;t you show me what you want to do?&quot;
											(Laughter)
